  "title": "Senior Resident Physician - KJ2",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Benefits Summary</strong></u></p><ul><li>Healthcare sector</li><li>Basic Up $9K (Resident Physician)</li><li>Basic Up $13K (Senior Resident Physician)</li><li>Full-Time Benefits Entitlements</li><li>Stable Career Opportunity</li><li>5 Day Work Week</li><li>Central Region Singapore<br /></li></ul><p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities and Duties</strong></u></p><p>The Clinical Services department is seeking candidates who are highly motivated for a fulfilling career as Senior Resident Physician/Resident Physician. The incumbent will be responsible for the daily running of ophthalmology clinics and any other ad-hoc duties assigned by his/her Supervisor or Head of Department. Employment will be on contract basis and will be renewable subject to performance.</p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u> </p><ul><li>Basic medical degree in the Second Schedule of the Medical Registration Act or postgraduate medical qualification registrable with the Singapore Medical Council</li><li>At least 3 years of ophthalmology practice experience</li><li>Highly adaptive and possesses excellent interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Must be able to do calls</li><li>Please note that the role does not have surgical privileges</li></ul><p><br />Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities.</p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by the company relating to this job application.</p><p>https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><strong>Kerlin Koh Jin Jiu</strong></p><p><strong>Registration Number: R25129773</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 06C2859 (MCI Career Services Pte Ltd)</strong></p>",
